'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 17''' was the 17th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Jawa's Corner]]
*[[Prequel Update]]
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[Don Bies]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 39}}
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[Trisha Biggar]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 40}}
*[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe]] &mdash; [[Richard LeParmentier]] {{C|[[Star Wars Insider 40|''Star Wars Insider'' 40]]}}

===Features===
*"[[I Bent My Wookiee! Celebrating the Star Wars/Simpsons Connection]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 38|''Star Wars Insider'' 38]]}}
*"[[Among the Clouds: An Audience with Billy Dee Williams]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 38}}
*"[[Terry Brooks: Sword of the Jedi]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 39|''Star Wars Insider'' 39]]}}
*"[[When Artoo Met Wicket]]" {{C|''Star Wars Insider'' 38}}
*"[[LucasArts: Behind the Magic]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 40|''Star Wars Insider'' 40]]}}
*"Facts, Figures and the Force"
*:<small>[[James Bennett]], the ''Star Wars'' group brand manager for [[Hasbro]] UK, answers collectors' questions.</small>
*"[[Big Deal]]"
*:<small>The second and final part of our guide to the [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|''Star Wars'' Customizable Card Game]].</small>
*Inside ''Star Wars''
*:<small>Highlights from the new Dorling Kindersley books ''[[Star Wars: The Visual Dictionary]]'' and ''[[Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections]]''.</small>

